## Hugo workflow
- Content in `content/posts/` (markdown)
- Frontmatter: title, date, draft, categories, tags, summary
- Images in `static/images/`
- Build: `hugo server -D` (preview) / `hugo` (prod)

## Operating instructions
- Adapt tone to target audience specified for each article
- Python/JS code: commented, incremental
- Document revisions: diff only, no full rewrites
